So feel free to ask questions at the end, and we'll get

22
00:01:30,039 --> 00:01:31,680
into a little bit of that later.

23
00:01:33,361 --> 00:01:34,882
So I'll introduce myself really quickly.

24
00:01:35,342 --> 00:01:37,004
My name is Lissette DeJu Montgomery.

25
00:01:37,024 --> 00:01:39,785
I have been an art director in the game industry for...

26
00:01:41,267 --> 00:01:42,688
I've been doing this for 21 years.

27
00:01:42,748 --> 00:01:44,389
I've been in leadership for over 10.

28
00:01:45,530 --> 00:01:47,291
I've worked at studios large and small,

29
00:01:47,551 --> 00:01:49,572
large studios like EA and Ubisoft,

30
00:01:50,533 --> 00:01:53,755
and small studios like Backbone and now Double Fine.

31
00:01:54,435 --> 00:01:57,657
I've worked on 14 different engines across multiple genres.

32
00:01:58,658 --> 00:02:00,239
Here's some of the ship titles that I made.

33
00:02:01,059 --> 00:02:03,661
Psychonauts 2 is also, of course, my why you're all here,

34
00:02:04,261 --> 00:02:06,202
but I've been making games for quite some time.

35
00:02:07,647 --> 00:02:09,968
In addition to making games for the last 20 years,

36
00:02:10,008 --> 00:02:11,908
I've also been an instructor at Gameheads.

37
00:02:12,008 --> 00:02:13,649
I see a few of my students here.

38
00:02:13,709 --> 00:02:15,570
Thank you.

