And so I'm very experienced at being in the classroom.

40
00:02:19,231 --> 00:02:20,292
And so I have a few rules.

41
00:02:20,632 --> 00:02:23,393
First rule is no cell phones or phone discussions

42
00:02:23,493 --> 00:02:24,253
during the talk.

43
